            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%93ai%E5%B0%88%E7%BE%8E%E6%96%BC%E5%89%8D-%E5%BE%A9%E8%8F%AF%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E8%82%A1%E5%82%B5%E9%9B%99%E6%94%B6%E5%82%98%E5%9E%8B%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E7%9E%84%E6%BA%96%E6%AD%90%E7%BE%8E%E6%97%A5%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD-124238330.html",
